data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! Living on the edge...next to peaceful agricultural land. Three times the average lot size (17,275 sqft) with walking trail right out the back door. Enjoy that country feeling yet close to shopping, schools, restaurants. This 1,800+ sqft home features NEW vinyl plank flooring in living areas, office/den with double glass doors, living room w/vaulted ceiling, kitchen & breakfast bar, light-filled dining area next to covered patio with cool custom-made planters; primary suite has large bath & walk-in closet. All appliances stay including nice washer & dryer. Hurry and schedule a showing. Don't miss this special opportunity!
